description:
Suitest instrumentation library for Xbox apps.

This package will make your Xbox app testable with Suitest. Suitest is a multi-platform end-to-end test automation service with the focus on the productivity and ease of use. Sign up for free at https://suite.st to get started.

To prepare your Xbox app for end-to-end testing with Suitest:

1. Add this package to your Xbox app dependencies.
2. In package.appxmanifest add these capabilities: Internet (Client & Server), Private Networks (Client & Server)
3. Add SuitestLibrary.Suitest.Initialize(); call near the end of your onLaunched() method in App.xaml.cs

Then upload the instrumented Xbox app package into Suitest and test away!

Happy testing!
summary: Suitest instrumentation library for Xbox apps.

description:
CppSharp is a tool and set of libraries which allows programmers to use C/C++ libraries with high-level programming languages (such as C#).

It is a tool that takes C/C++ header and library files and generates the necessary glue to surface the native API as a managed API. Such an API can be used to consume an existing native library in your high-level code or add scripting support to a native codebase.

The supported target languages at present are C# and C++/CLI.

It can also be used as a library to parse native code into a syntax tree with a rich declaration and type information model.

The NuGet version is Windows 64-bit only for the time being. Binary 32-bit releases for Windows can be found at https://github.com/mono/CppSharp/releases .
summary: CppSharp is a collection of libraries for working with C++ code from high-level languages.
